Place the SpaghettiOS GPG archive signing public key here.

To generate:
  gpg --full-generate-key  (use "SpaghettiOS Archive Signing Key" as name)
  gpg --export --armor <key-id> > config/archives/spaghettios.gpg

Include this file in the live-build configuration so the live system
can authenticate packages from the SpaghettiOS repository.
